{"arkId":"cl010361725","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010361725","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"vase","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Coupes peintes"},{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"vase"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Suse I (-4000 - -3500)","currentLocation":"Cambridge (Etats-Unis), Peabody Museum of Archaeology and Ethnology at Harvard University","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-4000,"endYear":-3500,"imprecision":"","text":"Suse I","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"A 6963","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"AS 15459","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"36-2-60\/7107","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"coupe\r\n\r\nPr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Coupe haute en forme de calice \u00e0 pied annulaire. La panse s\u0027\u00e9largit progressivement vers le haut. Le d\u00e9cor ext\u00e9rieur se limite \u00e0 un trait plein \u00e0 la base du pied. Le d\u00e9cor int\u00e9rieur, g\u00e9om\u00e9trique et animalier est de composition bipartite. Une croix de Malte, enferm\u00e9e dans un cercle, au centre de la coupe, est encadr\u00e9e de chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 par deux s\u00e9ries de petits zigzags ou W (\u00e9vocation de vols d\u0027oiseaux ?) ; sur chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9, en sym\u00e9trie, r\u00e9seaux de trois lignes bris\u00e9es enserrent un motif \u0022d\u0027animal-peigne\u0022 \u00e0 t\u00eate d\u0027oiseaux. En bordure, s\u00e9rie de dents de loup.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"10,3","displayDimension":"10,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"not